{{!-- The Archive dial's entries. Ghost 6 caps {{#get}} at 100 posts
     (limit="all" is gone), so the full set comes from stacked paged
     queries — 8 pages = 800-post capacity. Pages beyond the real
     total render nothing. ADD page="9" when the archive nears 800.
     Literal filters — {{#get}} can't interpolate. --}}
{{#get "posts" filter="tag:-[midnight-radio,dreams,art-diary,favorites,public-works]" limit="100" page="1" order="published_at desc"}}{{#foreach posts}}{{> "dial-entry"}}{{/foreach}}{{/get}}
